 19/2/18 Sell waterwheel . At 3o'c inspect the men and hors of the Regiment transport and got a good turnout . The hors are look well in spite of a reduc ration and our painter were at work on the limber . In the transport we have a number of elder men and they are a veri happi famili . Most countri chap they are great stay at home and amus themselv in their own littl circl . Know that they are on a good job they look to their behaviour and we get no order room case from them . After mess held a confer of my O.C. Coy Dooley Kennedi Fulton Mackinnon and discuss general . At mess we drank the King and the dinner was excel . Old Habel Cutler are a good pair .
